# Matrix — Project Configuration
# Format: name|path|mode|roles|description
#
# name:        Session name (unique identifier)
# path:        Absolute path to project directory (~ expands to $HOME)
# mode:        server (recommended) or interactive
# roles:       Comma-separated role names (interactive mode only)
# description: Short description shown in the Matrix UI
#
# Examples:
#   myproject|~/Projects/myproject|server||Web app for task management
#   myproject|~/Projects/myproject|interactive|planner,builder,tester|
#
# Add projects with: matrix add <name> <path>
# Set description:   matrix describe <name> <description>
# Remove with:       matrix remove <name>
